IMAPAccount personal
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User kuzey.koc7991@gmail.com
PassCmd "gopass savolla/mail/gmail/kuzey.koc7991@gmail.com app_pass_emacs"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-bundle.crt

IMAPStore personal-remote
Account personal

MaildirStore personal-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/area/mail/personal/
Inbox ~/area/mail/personal/Inbox

Channel personal
Far :personal-remote:
Near :personal-local:
Patterns * !Trash !Drafts
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
